Title: Jack's Kid

Summary: Jack gets a crash course in history, mythology, battle and parenthood. Wait- PARENTHOOD? Uh oh.

Title: Jack's Prison
Story 3/?
Author: Desiring Pirates
Summary: It was suppose to be a romantic night, until Jack was arrested. Now Liz has to trust someone she'd rather see dead. 
A/N: This is where we first meet Edward, who will soon become important. This also introduces the globe and it also test Elizabeth's faithfulness. This is also the first story that was more than three parts.

Title: Jack's Promise
Story 2/?
Author: DesiringPirates
Summary: Two months after Jack and Elizabeth's birthday, and they still have yet to call themselves official. This causes problems between them, and they make sail for England, so Liz can see her father. Meanwhile, Ana Maria feels smothered.
A/N: This is the story before the plot actually starts happening. Building Jack and Liz's relationship, and such other things.
